Bet. $300.000.

242
00:29:34.093 --> 00:29:36.063
Call.

243
00:29:37.523 --> 00:29:39.503
And call.

244
00:29:43.163 --> 00:29:45.373
Three players.

245
00:29:48.653 --> 00:29:50.633
Check.

246
00:29:54.433 --> 00:29:56.403
Monsieur Bond?

247
00:30:05.013 --> 00:30:07.183
Bet $500.000.

248
