Look. its the tank. he's bluffing.

249
00:30:23.003 --> 00:30:24.983
My God. James was right.

250
00:30:26.073 --> 00:30:28.053
It's up to you.

251
00:30:33.883 --> 00:30:35.863
Raise. $1 million.

252
00:30:42.883 --> 00:30:45.253
Seem someone know something I don't.

253
00:30:46.243 --> 00:30:48.623
Fold. Heads-up. gentlemen.

254
00:30:49.263 --> 00:30:51.243
It's up to you.

255
00:31:04.243 --> 00:31:06.223
Two.

256
00:31:06.613 --> 00:31:08.593
Will raise. $2 million.

257
00:31:10.573 --> 00:31:12.553
It's up to you.

258
00:31:23.033 --> 00:31:25.003
I'm all in.

259
00:31:32.033 --> 00:31:35.983
Well it's $14.5 millioner. It is up to you. monsieur Bond.

260
00:31:39.343 --> 00:31:43.303
Bond will have to call all in to call his bluff.

261
00:31:44.293 --> 00:31:46.263
- Call. - Call.

262
00:31:47.113 --> 00:31:49.083
Gentlemen. showdown. please.

263
00:31:51.313 --> 00:31:53.483
Full house. kings and aces.

264
00:31:53.783 --> 00:31:55.763
Monsieur Le Chiffre?

265
00:32:08.273 --> 00:32:12.223
It's four checks. Monsieur Le Chiffre wins.

266
00:32:15.443 --> 00:32:18.113
You thought I was bluffing. mr. Bond.

267
00:32:20.823 --> 00:32:22.803
Please. we now break for one hour.

268
00:32:22.853 --> 00:32:26.813
When we return. big blind will be $200.000.

269
00:33:01.713 --> 00:33:05.663
I'm gonna need the other $5 million to buy me back in.

270
00:33:05.673 --> 00:33:07.653
I can't do that. James.

271
00:33:08.343 --> 00:33:10.323
Look. I made a mistake.

272
00:33:11.403 --> 00:33:14.373
I was impatient. maybe I was arrogant. but I can beat him.

273
00:33:14.573 --> 00:33:18.323
- I'm sorry - Sorry? Sorry?

274
00:33:18.333 --> 00:33:21.493
Why aren't you putting that in a sentence.
like maybe. "sorry that Le Chiffre wins. -

275
00:33:21.693 --> 00:33:24.463
- continuing terrorism and killing innocent people."

276
00:33:24.653 --> 00:33:28.713
You lost because of your ego. And your ego can't take it.

277
00:33:28.913 --> 00:33:32.573
- All you're going to do now is loose more. -
Well then you're an idiot.

278
00:33:32.763 --> 00:33:36.723
- I'm sorry? - I said you're a bloody idiot.

279
00:33:37.413 --> 00:33:39.393
Look in my eyes.

280
00:33:40.233 --> 00:33:42.213
I can beat this man. You know that.

281
00:33:44.383 --> 00:33:46.163
Put your hand off my arm.

282
